The school I worked in got rid of them at least 15 years ago, and actually at that time, they would have been called "chalkboards", since they were green.  Actual blackboards went out around here maybe 25 years ago or more.  

I'm sure you can still find either one somewhere in the world, or even in this area, but "obsolescent" is perfectly fine for the clue.

